{"tid":2148903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美中情局報告：無證據顯示中國政府已獲取TikTok美國用戶資料","createTime":"2020-08-10T06:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T02:55:23.000Z","uid":159448,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5253c2d0817eb4c3603145711daa2ab731c358a7","tid":2148903,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"美國媒體8月7日稱，中央情報局（Central Intelligence Agency，CIA）近期一份報告指，沒有證據顯示中國政府已獲取社交應用程式TikTok（抖音海外版）的美國用戶資料。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》指，中央情報局的分析師告訴白宮，也許中國情報部門能攔截用戶的數據或者透過TikTok來入侵其智能手機，不過並無證據顯示他們曾做過這樣的事。<br />\n<br />\n報道還引述智能手機保安公司Lookout安全情報研究總監Christoph Hebeisen表示，他們檢查TikTok後得出的結論與中情局差不多，即中國政府似乎無權獲得美國用戶的數據，但倘若北京想要，也有可能得到它。<br />\n<br />\n他就此解釋，TikTok收集用戶資料的方法與美國科技公司差不多，華府在獲得《外國情報監視法》的許可令後也能從美國社交媒體公司獲得用戶資料。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/508926/%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%AD%E6%83%85%E5%B1%80%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E7%84%A1%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B7%B2%E7%8D%B2%E5%8F%96tiktok%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F508926%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%258F%2596tiktok%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=f41e2d44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/508926/%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%AD%E6%83%85%E5%B1%80%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E7%84%A1%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B7%B2%E7%8D%B2%E5%8F%96tiktok%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">CIA都比中共收買左</span>"},{"pid":"c525d7253ca816e5840576a81ed35353d121f49d","tid":2148903,"uid":143343,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a38722df2e39e78e396ed9dd37e6b8ea376e877d","tid":2148903,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdd239e0cbe4ffcaa15e208859ebd48d16313bb","tid":2148903,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c525d7253ca816e5840576a81ed35353d121f49d","tid":2148903,"uid":143343,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"起完快啲幫手追擊CIA"},{"pid":"4e20675cffdae29cbf650d37decd7e0b48761631","tid":2148903,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"HK01？"},{"pid":"f9018b2251eb4da0e2fe1e0d5d4da613af11314f","tid":2148903,"uid":288675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:03:15.000Z","msg":"not proved doesn't means not happened"},{"pid":"d9d76b41e0cb4d358da1cfc668669046fb06d900","tid":2148903,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:04:42.000Z","msg":"Not the point"},{"pid":"1ef8fbe545774481e3390bafc14a348632a97bf9","tid":2148903,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4e20675cffdae29cbf650d37decd7e0b48761631","tid":2148903,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"HK01？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:04:52.000Z","msg":"佢只係引述"},{"pid":"f4f3d757ffcb03a2bdf02261aa61da03bee0cbd3","tid":2148903,"uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"在港被招攬做中國間諜　收 650 萬元　前中情局人員李振成認罪判囚 19 年<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.c